node.text:
Yo I just want to take a moment to say a big motherfucking THANK YOU to each and every one of you who has supported me on this musical journey. 

I can’t tell you how much your sweet words and the continued streams mean to me. 

Thank you thank you thank you thank you 

If you haven’t already, be sure to go check out my new songs on @spotify

Over here feeling like the luckiest sun of a gun on the planet getting to do so much of what I love in one life time 

 Xo
Jasimi

node.text:
Just over here prioritizing my healing 🤘🏾 

Real talk though. 
Therapy is an extremely powerful tool. This season in my life is focused largely on rest and healing old trauma (that I don’t need to get into cuz there’s over a million of y’all that I 👏🏾 don’t 👏🏾 know 😂)
The point I’m trying to make is that it’s not linear or easy or always pretty, but when the joy does hit it hits different. Brighter. Lighter. Fuller. 
Lately I’ve been thinking of my mental/ emotional/ spiritual health as the house I will live in for the rest of my life. 
I’m laying each brick with care, cleaning all the debris away and decorating with things that I find beautiful and inspiring. 
anyhoo… 

Healing is sexy. It’s the best gift you can give to yourself. 
✌🏾

Bless up!
